title: S17 Ep69: Trading Spooky Stories Around The Campfire w/Jim Harold
itunes:title: Trading Spooky Stories Around The Campfire w/Jim Harold
description:
On today's Darkness Radio, we are Trading Spooky Stories Around The Campfire With Podcaster, Jim Harold!

After such a warm response to Jim just a few weeks ago here on the show, we wanted to bring him back, fire up the old digital campfire, and give the Darkness Radio listeners a taste of what Jim does on Jim Harold's Campfire!

Sit back, relax, turn down the lights, and sit around the warm digital glow of your device as Jim tells real life stories of the paranormal along with his listeners on this special edition of the show!

and a reminder that you can listen to episodes of Jim Harold's Campfire on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, or wherever you are listening to this episode of Darkness Radio!
